，他们使用人工智能来确定一个聪明的解决方案</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/mathematicians-puzzled-over-a-famous-problem-for-80-years-now-theyve-used-ai-to-identify-a-clever-solution-180988889/</link><description>1946 年，数学家 Paul Erdős 提出了单位距离问题，并提出了获胜策略。一种人工智能模型现在已经找到了更好的模型。为什么人类没有先到达那里？</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 16:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/mathematicians-puzzled-over-a-famous-problem-for-80-years-now-theyve-used-ai-to-identify-a-clever-solution-180988889/</guid></item><item><title>巴黎圣母院火灾后的考古挖掘揭示了巴黎几个世纪历史的秘密</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/secrets-from-centuries-of-paris-history-are-emerging-from-archaeological-digs-after-the-notre-dame-cathedral-fire-180988886/</link><description>在围绕标志性哥特式地标进行计划重建之前，研究人员正在通过中世纪和罗马层面挖掘这座城市的过去</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 14:13:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/secrets-from-centuries-of-paris-history-are-emerging-from-archaeological-digs-after-the-notre-dame-cathedral-fire-180988886/</guid></item><item><title>考古学家在西班牙一座修道院的挖掘中发现了一位 14 世纪女王的遗骸以及埋错坟墓的多具骸骨</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/archaeologists-excavating-a-monastery-in-spain-identified-the-remains-of-a-14th-century-queen-and-multiple-skeletons-buried-in-the-wrong-graves-180988877/</link><description>蒙卡达埃利森达墓长期以来一直令专家们着迷。但研究小组惊讶地发现，据称属于中世纪骑士和女修道院院长的墓葬中埋葬的是完全不同的人</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 13:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/archaeologists-excavating-a-monastery-in-spain-identified-the-remains-of-a-14th-century-queen-and-multiple-skeletons-buried-in-the-wrong-graves-180988877/</guid></item><item><title>鸽子如何找到回家的路？新研究表明鸟类卓越的导航技能来自它们的肝脏</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/how-do-pigeons-find-their-way-home-new-research-suggests-the-birds-remarkable-navigational-skills-come-from-their-livers-180988884/</link><description>在